Debug info
Before moving on, to implement a camera frustum i want to add some debug info to the scene. Nameley, i want to know how many objects are rendered. I&#39;m actually going to provide all the code for this, just follow along. This is actually pretty simple, we start with the most basic thing that&#39;s being rendered.
In OBJ.cs, change the Render method of the OBJ class from this (taken from your github):
public void Render() {
    GL.PushMatrix();
    //always getter
    GL.MultMatrix(WorldMatrix.OpenGL);
    if (model != null) {
        model.Render();
    }
    GL.PopMatrix();
